Objective

To demonstrate container-to-container communication and perform basic database operations (Create, Insert, Select) using Flask and MySQL.

🔹 Step 1: Create Docker Network
              docker network create mynetwork
🔹 Step 2: Run MySQL Container
              docker run -d --name mysql --sql:5.7
🔹 Step 3: Create Flask Application from app.py

🔹 Step 4: Create requirements.txt
            flask
            mysql-connector-python

🔹 Step 5: Create Dockerfile

🔹 Step 6: Build Flask Image
          docker build -t flaskapp .

🔹 Step 7: Run Flask Container
          docker run -d --name flaskapp --network mynetwork -p 5000:5000 flaskapp

🔹 Step 8: Verify Containers
          docker ps

🔹 Step 9: Access Application
            
            Open browser:
            
            http://localhost:5000
